	<text xml:lang="de">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salus per Christum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Statueramus communem ad te dare epistolam, charissime frater, <persName ref="p20" cert="high">Thomas</persName><note target="fn3" type="footnote"/> scilicet, Cuͦnradus<note target="fn4" type="footnote"/> et ego, sed negotia non contemnenda fecerunt, quo minus hoc factum sit.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc <persName ref="p20" cert="high">Thomas</persName> abiturus cum uxore <persName ref="p19" cert="high">Ambrosii</persName><note target="fn5" type="footnote"/> hanc, quam hic vides, epistolam dedit eamque jussit, ut legerem, deinde obsignatam tibi mitterem<note target="fn6" type="footnote"/>.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Caeterum fratris<note target="fn7" type="footnote"/> et meam mentem plane non potui iam ad te scribere.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Proxime satis tibi fiet<note target="fn8" type="footnote"/>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><pb type="edition" next="234"/>Quo minus autem succenseas tarditati meae, en mitto literas <persName ref="p28" cert="high">Buceri</persName> ad consulem <placeName ref="l70" cert="high">Augustanum</placeName><note target="fn9" type="footnote"/>, ex quibus intelliges forte, quo fructu cum optimo viro contulerimus<note target="fn10" type="footnote"/>.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dann man möchte in dem Fall auch wohl quackeln<note target="fn11" type="footnote"/>.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Das wäre aber gut deutsch gerettet.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cave<note target="fna" type="footnote"/> autem, ne spargatur epistola, deinde per hunc tabellionem<note target="fn12" type="footnote"/> remitte.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nullum enim exemplar est mihi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribit <persName ref="p891" cert="high">Froschouerus</persName><note target="fn13" type="footnote"/> de quadam praefatione in germanolatinum testamentum<note target="fn14" type="footnote"/>.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc quid sibi velit, non intelligo.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nescio, quid bonum virum moveat, cum tot sint apud vos millies ad hanc rem aptiores.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Mein Bruder, Vetter Thoma und ich sucht gern, dass Ihr ein Mal gegen Stein spazierten, dann wir wollten zu Euch kommen <foreign xml:lang="la">neglectis omnibus negotiis,</foreign> wann Ihr nun lustig werden<note target="fn15" type="footnote"/> zu spacieren.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Wir hatten auch wohl viel zu reden, nicht Fabelwerk<note target="fn16" type="footnote"/>.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Wollte Gott, dass ich möglich wäre!</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Ohne Adresse.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
